The paper deals with distributed algorithms for backup placement and their applications to maximum matching approximation and self-stabilization. This falls under the categories of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Algorithms (cs.AL).
